N2  - The article presents news briefs relating to members of the Academy of Management, including an announcement that Clark E. Myers, dean of the School of Business Administration at the University of Miami, has been named dean of Emory University's School of Business Administration, Richard F. Barton became a professor of management in the School of Business Administration at the Texas Technological College, and that Dr. Charles R. Holloman, an Associate Professor at the Air Force Academy, has been promoted to Lt. Colonel in the U.S. Air Force.
